{"tid":1974850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"司法覆核監警會越權查示威 高等法院裁定敗訴","createTime":"2020-04-16T06:42:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T13:29:24.000Z","uid":311198,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"03fe1632cfdbd3882e90e971cec07f76f3b8de62","tid":1974850,"uid":311198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T06:42:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200416/RFTPFP5ICDZDBXVIVTYWK4VCK4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200416%2FRFTPFP5ICDZDBXVIVTYWK4VCK4%2F&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgGWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=3368cd4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200416%2FRFTPFP5ICDZDBXVIVTYWK4VCK4%2F&h=a1fa5ae4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200416/RFTPFP5ICDZDBXVIVTYWK4VCK4/</a>"},{"pid":"fe36b4d8cacf9d97d387c6fe5b890df5f5029605","tid":1974850,"uid":311198,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T06:43:09.000Z","msg":"監警會去年7月對反送中運動展開調查，一直被政府用作拒絕成立獨立調查委員會的藉口。社工呂智恆及後提出司法覆核，指監警會（IPCC）職能不包括主動調查事件，質疑監警會「尋找事實」屬越權。案件早前於高等法院以視像會議系統遙距進行審訊，法官今午頒下判詞，駁回呂的申請，並要呂支付監警會訟費。"},{"pid":"cd8e6576947b99f7e3d6bd5771b51fe93e3f1c94","tid":1974850,"uid":311198,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T06:43:30.000Z","msg":"代表呂智恆的資深大狀於審訊時指，立法會當年在審議《獨立監察警方處理投訴委員會條例》時，清楚界定調查事件的責任在於投訴警察課，監警會不應作獨立調查。他舉例指，若市民投訴警察在執勤期間使用過份武力，而投訴警察課和監警會皆對同一事件進行調查，有可能會得出互相矛盾的結果，這並不是立法的原意。<br />\n惟代表監警會的資深大狀黃繼明則指，監警會對反送中事件並非「尋找事實」，只是希望了解事件發生的時序和背景，繼而審視投訴警察課的工作，是事實「裁斷」，角色與警察投訴課沒有重疊，更不會造成事實矛盾。"},{"pid":"7172820bf9c9b3cc0964b3abda33df66c5a3e1e1","tid":1974850,"uid":311198,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T06:44:57.000Z","msg":"判詞：<a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/doc/judg/word/vetted/other/en/2019/HCAL002924A_2019.docx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Fdoc%2Fjudg%2Fword%2Fvetted%2Fother%2Fen%2F2019%2FHCAL002924A_2019.docx&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgGWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=8747ece7\" target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/doc/judg/word/vetted/other/en/2019/HCAL002924A_2019.docx</a>"},{"pid":"b2e9e5c83520e8655200d2f1fbff78d912b2b15c","tid":1974850,"uid":54959,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T06:46:51.000Z","msg":"屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99542424301538858ad1aa5783d5560ec8ff5479","tid":1974850,"uid":124180,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T06:49:36.000Z","msg":"已經冇嘢制衡到呢場人禍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45f47926b4efe4e8cb13fb56bd01d3609ab63583","tid":1974850,"uid":39974,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T06:52:11.000Z","msg":"睇唔明佢司法覆核黎做乜"},{"pid":"fe10859aa9d127ba3ddaa46054f935366a973540","tid":1974850,"uid":32722,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T06:54:22.000Z","msg":"咁監警會可以出佢份死人報告未?"},{"pid":"9f692e8aefba48bd48e6e7fc46794b01afb1dab6","tid":1974850,"uid":312526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T06:56:50.000Z","msg":"唔明"},{"pid":"087181f55e7a80bc85cdab5704cdb9ac364116b8","tid":1974850,"uid":112581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45f47926b4efe4e8cb13fb56bd01d3609ab63583","tid":1974850,"uid":39974,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T06:52:11.000Z","msg":"睇唔明佢司法覆核黎做乜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T06:57:40.000Z","msg":"司法上證明冇野阻止到班狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有官話點解唔搵監狗會個時可以名正言順屌佢老母"},{"pid":"94bf1bdaf969b7eabb7cf1211db77c4070f65e99","tid":1974850,"uid":311198,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"45f47926b4efe4e8cb13fb56bd01d3609ab63583","tid":1974850,"uid":39974,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T06:52:11.000Z","msg":"睇唔明佢司法覆核黎做乜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T06:57:46.0